<heading>inspect - Inspect a box in detail.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>inspect NAME</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Shows details of a named box at the current world level: its description, portable items it contains and notes attached to it.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>inspect Desk
  Inspect the box called Desk.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>look, go, place, take</paragraph>
